01:29:11.153 --> 01:29:14.145
- Nice try.
- Get lost.

01:29:14.222 --> 01:29:16.986
Lane, you really are the best.

01:29:26.601 --> 01:29:29.968
- We've been worried about you.
- What are you doing up here?

01:29:30.038 --> 01:29:32.472
Do you know how long a drive
it is to get here?

01:29:32.541 --> 01:29:34.406
Get her skis.
We're goin' home.

01:29:35.877 --> 01:29:38.038
Excuse me.

01:29:39.114 --> 01:29:43.517
This was a sublime metamorphosis
of the Lane Myer...

01:29:43.585 --> 01:29:46.145
I think the crowds
were expecting to see here...

01:29:46.221 --> 01:29:48.712
at Brody Mountain today.

01:29:48.790 --> 01:29:51.987
Perhaps you can tell us
what brought on...

01:29:52.060 --> 01:29:54.494
such an enchanting,
exhilarating fate?

01:29:55.497 --> 01:29:57.431
Language lessons.

01:30:02.404 --> 01:30:03.996
Language lessons.

01:30:05.140 --> 01:30:09.668
Inspired words from a man
who knows how to ski.

01:30:09.744 --> 01:30:12.076
You're nothing but a little tramp,
you know.

01:30:12.147 --> 01:30:15.981
I don't know what Ricky
even sees in you.

01:30:16.051 --> 01:30:18.076
- What are you doing with her?
- She's coming with me.

01:30:18.153 --> 01:30:20.053
- She's coming with us.
- Wrong.

01:30:20.121 --> 01:30:23.613
You would be wise
to do as Mother says, Myer.

01:30:23.692 --> 01:30:26.126
Do something to him.

01:30:38.006 --> 01:30:39.701
Son of a bitch!

01:30:41.876 --> 01:30:43.935
Come on, honey!
Nail the sucker!

01:30:45.380 --> 01:30:48.144
What are you doing to him?

01:30:48.216 --> 01:30:51.413
Come on. That's a boy.

01:30:57.993 --> 01:30:59.927
Come on.

01:32:16.938 --> 01:32:19.270
Ricky, where are you going?

